	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you require positive leading (ascenders cannot touch previous line's descenders), and you use CHR RAM, you could do a lot worse than <a href="https://github.com/pinobatch/rhde-nes/blob/master/tilesets/vwf7.png" class="postlink">this 7-pixel-tall proportional font</a>, which I used in RHDE, robotfindskitten, the Action 53 menu, and the NES port of 240p Test Suite.<br /><br /><img src="https://pineight.com/mw/images/b/b2/Lorem_ipsum_NES_VWF.png" alt="Image" /><br />Sample of translated Lorem ipsum text

		

		</td>
	</tr>
